trans-unit.source: Contains values that specify changes in the structure of the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uiautomation](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-uiautomation-md.md)] element tree.
trans-unit.target: Содержит значения, которые определяют изменения в структуре [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uiautomation](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-uiautomation-md.md)] дерево элементов.

trans-unit.source: A child element was added to the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)] element tree.
trans-unit.target: Дочерний элемент был добавлен [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)] дерево элементов.

trans-unit.source: A child element was removed from the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)] element tree.
trans-unit.target: Дочерний элемент был удален из [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)] дерево элементов.

trans-unit.source: Child elements were added to the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)] element tree.
trans-unit.target: Дочерние элементы были добавлены [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)] дерево элементов.

trans-unit.source: Child elements were removed from the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)] element tree.
trans-unit.target: Дочерние элементы были удалены из [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)] дерево элементов.

trans-unit.source: Child elements were invalidated in the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)] element tree.
trans-unit.target: Дочерние элементы стали недействительными в [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)] дерево элементов.

trans-unit.source: This might mean that one or more children were added or removed, depending on the UI Automation providers implementation.
trans-unit.target: Это может означать, что один или несколько дочерних элементов были добавлены или удалены, в зависимости от реализации поставщиков автоматизации пользовательского интерфейса.

trans-unit.source: The order of the child elements in the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)] element tree changed.
trans-unit.target: Порядок дочерних элементов в [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)] изменить дерево элементов.
